To streamline the account opening process, we need to:

1. Define models to store account opening requests.
2. Create services to handle the creation and processing of these requests.
3. Implement controllers to manage API endpoints for account opening.
4. Update the routes to expose these endpoints.

Epic Title: Account Opening and Service Modifications

We will create necessary files within the `backend/account/opening_requests` directory to manage account opening requests and update the existing project structure.

